OL,3,COff-grid bus that Swansea family used
OL,4,Cto travel the world is up for sale
OL,6,FA family from Swansea is selling the
OL,7,Fbeloved bus they used to travel the
OL,8,Fworld and live off-grid.
OL,10,FThe bus, named Skooby, was used by
OL,11,Fschools in Oklahoma until July 2018.
OL,12,FChris and Tracy Margetts purchased it
OL,13,Fand imported it to the UK.
OL,15,FThe couple had the vehicle shot
OL,16,Fblasted, re-painted and rewired. Their
OL,17,Fchildren named the bus 'Skooby'.
