OL,3,COff-grid bus that Swansea family used
OL,4,Cto travel the world is up for sale
OL,6,F"Every time I get on it, I can't help
OL,7,Fbut smile", Chris said, "you look up
OL,8,Fand down the bus and look at all the
OL,9,Fcool stuff and just remember all the
OL,10,Fplaces you've been".
OL,12,FThey used Skooby to tour Europe and
OL,13,Fthen had her shipped back to the
OL,14,FStates where she travelled across the
OL,15,Fcontinent of North America and down to
OL,16,FMexico and back.
OL,18,FSkooby arrived back in the UK in June
OL,19,Fthis year and is now up for sale.
