OL,4,Cto travel the world is up for sale
OL,6,FWhen Scooby is on the road she guzzles
OL,7,Fquite a bit of gas with her 7.2 litre
OL,8,Fcaterpillar C7 diesel engine.
OL,10,FShe also offers a range of home
OL,11,Fcomforts including a wood-burning
OL,12,Fstove, toilet and shower, and air
OL,13,Fconditioning. And there's plenty of
OL,14,Froom with bunks plus a super king bed.
OL,16,FThe home on wheels could be yours for
OL,17,Fjust under #75,000.
